:p How do you manage your time effectively during the ASVAB?
??x
Time management involves pacing yourself so that you can complete all sections of the test within the given timeframe. A good strategy is to allocate a specific amount of time per question, ensuring you don't spend too much time on any single item.

For example, if you have 75 minutes for one section and there are 100 questions, aim to spend about 45 seconds per question.
```java
public class TimeManagement {
